<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ق ر أ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣٩٧١ - ق ر أ]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أقرأَ يُقرئ، إقراءً، فهو مُقْرِئ، والمفعول مُقْرَأ <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• أقرأتِ المرأةُ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - حاضَت.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ - طهُرت.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">• أقرأ الشَّخْصَ:</span> جعله يَقْرَأُ <span class="c1">"أقرأ التِّلميذَ الدرسَ"</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">• أقرأه القُرْآنَ:</span> عَلَّمه قواعِدَ قراءتِهِ <span class="c1">" <span class="c3">{سَنُقْرِئُكَ فَلاَ تَنْسَى}</span> "</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">• أقرأه السَّلامَ:</span> أبْلَغَه إيّاه <span class="c1">"أقرِئ محمّدًا السَّلامَ"</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>